OL,6,FA mother from Kendal whose baby boy
OL,7,Fdied a month after he was born
OL,8,Fpremature is raising money for a new
OL,9,Fsensory room in the hospital where she
OL,10,Fwas treated.
OL,12,F19-year-old Caitlen Clayton gave birth
OL,13,Fto her son Arthur when she was just 28
OL,14,Fweeks pregnant - making him three
OL,15,Fmonths premature.
