OL,6,FShe said: "They said to me that either
OL,7,Fhe will have passed away in my tummy
OL,8,For he'll pass away during delivery,
OL,9,Fand if he passes away in delivery I'll
OL,10,Fbe asleep, so I'll never meet him
OL,11,Falive."
OL,13,FArthur defied the odds, and was born
OL,14,Fon July 26.
OL,16,FCaitlen said: "I remember meeting him
OL,17,Ffor the first time, and I put my hand
OL,18,Fon his toes, and he was wiggling his
OL,19,Ftoes on my hand.
