OL,6,F"He had these really big eyes, and
OL,7,Fevery nurse who looked at him was
OL,8,Flike, 'what big eyes he has. He has
OL,9,Fproper really big eyes.'"
OL,11,FDespite Arthur's triumph, surviving
OL,12,Fbeing born three months premature, he
OL,13,Fweighed just 400g.
OL,15,FHis lungs were not strong enough to
OL,16,Fget oxygen to his heart, and his heart
OL,17,Fwasn't strong enough to pump the
OL,18,Foxygen around the rest of his body.
OL,20,FArthur died a month later, on August
OL,21,F24.
