OL,6,FCaitlen said: "I wouldn't wish it upon
OL,7,Fmy worst enemy.
OL,9,F"Losing a child, I think, is the worst
OL,10,Fthing anyone can ever go through."
OL,12,FCaitlen is raising money for the
OL,13,FNeonatal Intensive Care Unit (NICU) at
OL,14,FRoyal Preston Hospital where she and
OL,15,FArthur were treated.
