OL,6,FShe's hoping to create 'Arthur's
OL,7,Fplayroom' - a sensory room with toys
OL,8,Ffor babies and their siblings and
OL,9,Ffamilies. She also wants to get the
OL,10,Frooms on the ward to be redecorated to
OL,11,Ffeel less medical, and more baby-
OL,12,Ffriendly.
OL,14,FShe said: "I want to give him what he
OL,15,Fdeserves and show everyone how
OL,16,Fincredibly proud I am of him as well.
