OL,6,F"Knowing that I've got other mums and
OL,7,Fother dads messaging me saying thank
OL,8,Fyou for doing what you're doing, my
OL,9,Fbaby could have really used that when
OL,10,Fthey were in the NICU, these kind of
OL,11,Fmessages really carry me on and lift
OL,12,Fme up when I feel bit helpless.
OL,14,FCaitlen's fundraiser has already
OL,15,Fraised over a thousand pounds, but is
OL,16,Fstill receiving donations to her
OL,17,Ffundraising page, as she tries to
OL,18,Fcreate the best space possible for
OL,19,Ffamilies who have to visit the NICU.
